data.description: Assumable loan of 5.375 on this home. Fantastic home located in highly sought after subdivision Stirling Bridge. In between Samsung and Applied Materials, within 17 minutes to Tesla. Close to Toll Road 130 and Hwy 290 and Parmer Lane. Home is located on a corner lot for extra yard space, This home has been recently remodeled with new laminate flooring throughout. New roof. New paint though all interior. New stove and refrigerator conveys. Island in kitchen. Covered back patio with new ceiling fan. Open floor plan with large living room. Garage has new epoxy painted floor with flakes as well as freshly painted garage walls. In law floor plan. Has brick on 3 sides of home for energy efficiency. Home is move in ready. Like new, just bring furniture and clothes and family.  Hurry, will not last!!!
